videos.headline: Alabama takes big loss when fumble goes out-of-bounds
videos.description: Alabama's Jacob Coker is chased down by Michigan State's Arjen Colquhoun who knocks the ball out of the QB's hands, but the Spartans are unable to recover when the ball is kicked out of bounds.

videos.headline: Alabama connects on deep pass for 50-yard gain
videos.description: Alabama's Jacob Coker heaves it deep to Calvin Ridley who hauls it in for the 50-yard pick up at the one yard line.

videos.headline: Alabama opens the scoring with one-yard TD
videos.description: Alabama's Heisman Trophy winner Derrick Henry takes the handoff and plunges into the end zone from one yard out to give Alabama the first lead of the game, 7-0.

videos.headline: Alabama into scoring range with 41-yard pickup
videos.description: Alabama's Jacob Coker finds O.J. Howard streaking down the field for the 41-yard catch and run that would set up a field goal for the Crimson Tide.

videos.headline: Jones' INT kills Spartans' drive at the goal line
videos.description: Driving deep in Alabama territory late in the first half, Connor Cook is picked off by Cyrus Jones at the goal line to keep Michigan State scoreless heading into halftime.

videos.headline: Cyrus Jones takes punt 57 yards to the house
videos.description: Alabama's Cyrus Jones finds a seam on the punt return and breaks a tackle to weave his way into the end zone and increase the Crimson Tide's lead to 24-0.

videos.headline: Ridley's 2nd TD turning Cotton Bowl into rout
videos.description: Alabama's Jacob Coker hits Calvin Ridley on the post route for the Crimson Tide's third touchdown of the third quarter to give them a commanding 31-0 lead over Michigan State.

videos.headline: C. Cook pass incomplete on 4th down

videos.headline: These Michigan State faces say it all
videos.description: The looks on the faces of Michigan State fans, as well as coach Mark Dantonio, tell the story of this year's Goodyear Cotton Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (These Michigan State faces say it all) 2015/12/31 PVC

videos.headline: Drake busts loose for 58-yard run
videos.description: Alabama's Kenyan Drake sweeps right and then cuts back left, avoiding all the tacklers to the 10 yard line for a 58-yard gain.

videos.headline: Henry's nasty stiff-arm leads to 2nd TD
videos.description: Alabama's Derrick Henry throws a vicious stiff-arm to fight off a defender before finding the end zone for his second touchdown of the night, increasing the Crimson Tide lead to 38-0.
